name: Rocket Jump (itch) (carsonifyy)
description:
Made for Low Effort Jam 22

as a challenge for myself, I also made this game in under 3 hours - from concept to exporting the game

Play as Rocket the cat to reach the top of the tower and grab some tasty tuna, simply click with your mouse where you want to jump to, but be careful, you will fall a lot

---- side note ----

this game is REALLY HARD and really ANNOYING
